                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"> <locus target="#116rb">f. 116rb</locus>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">  ዝመጽሐፍ፡
                                 ዘአንበሰት፡ ዘአቡነ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ዘሰርቃ (sic)፡ ወዘተአገላ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለኩን (sic)፡ በቃለ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡
                                 ወጳውሎስ፡</q>
                              <q xml:lang="en"> This is a book (belonging to the church) of
                                 ʾAnbasat, of ʾabuna Libānos. He who stole it or took it by violence
                                 shall be excommunicated by the word of Peter and Paul.</q>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2"> <locus target="#117ra">f. 117ra</locus>: <desc type="MagicFormula">Magic incantation.<quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                              <quote xml:lang="en"/> The note vontains several magical names
                              (ʾasmāt).</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3"> <locus target="#117rb">f. 117rb</locus>: <desc type="GuestText">Prayer of St Mary (Lk. 1:46-55).<quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                              <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#117va">f. 117va</locus>: <desc type="ProtectivePrayer">Unidentified prayer.<quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                              <quote xml:lang="en"/> Crudely written, end part poorly
                              legible.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The Text in the columns has been entirely or partly
                           outlined with a pencil (?): <locus from="57v" to="58r">57v-58r</locus>,
                           61v, 66v-67r:
 </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">-Crude notes: <locus target="#12r">12r</locus> (in dark
                           red ink); 43r, 46r, 66v
 </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3"> - Crude drawings, possibly of geometrical figures: <locus target="#102r">102r</locus>. 
 </item>
                        <item xml:id="e4"> - <locus target="#116v">116v</locus>: Traces of an erased
                           text are still visible. Crude note in violet ink at the bottom of the
                           page.</item>
                     </list>
